=head1 DESCRIPTION

Information about the automation option based on a rule category for a
single select question.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Category => Str

The category name, as defined in Rules.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Condition => Str

The condition to apply for the automation option. If the condition is
C<PRESENT>, then the option is applied when the contact data includes
the category. Similarly, if the condition is C<NOT_PRESENT>, then the
option is applied when the contact data does not include the category.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> OptionRefId => Str

The identifier of the answer option.



